videos.description: Kipper Nichols intercepts a bad Buckeyes pass and takes it all  the way to the rim for the flush.
videos.headline: Illinois' Nichols turns defense into offense

videos.description: Keita Bates-Diop runs the floor and secures an offensive putback for the Buckeyes.
videos.headline: Ohio State's Bates-Diop hustles for basket

videos.description: Keita Bates-Diop owns the paint in the second half getting a turnaround jumper to drop.
videos.headline: Ohio State's Bates-Diop does work in the paint

videos.description: Mark Alstork takes Ohio State's inbound pass the other way and lays in the easy bucket.
videos.headline: Illinois' Alstork steals inbound pass

videos.description: Trent Frazier blows by his defender with a nifty move and sinks a pretty floater in the second half.
videos.headline: Illinois' Frazier drops in floater

videos.description: Kaleb Wesson gets an offensive rebound and seals it for the Buckeyes with a putback layup against Illinois.
videos.headline: Ohio State's Wesson hits dagger
